	    <m id="3809">kích</m>
	  </w>
	  <w>
	    <m id="6381">vaa</m>
	  </w>
	  <w>
	    <m id="3999">kúnish</m>
	  </w>
	  <w gl="kind of make">
	    <m id="3970">kumée</m>
	    <m id="2357">kyav</m>
	  </w>,
	  <w gl="the white man">
	    <m id="4407">pa</m>
	    <m id="500">'apxantîich</m>
	  </w>
	  <w>
	    <m id="1670">îin</m>
	  </w>
	  <w gl="he has said to us">
	    <m id="5506">ta</m>
	    <m id="3841">kin</m>
	    <m id="2733">ipêer</m></w>.</kar>
	<eng>Of all the Karuk plants not one is the kind of make like that of the tobacco plant; only the black nightshade is that kind of make, the whiteman tells us.</eng>
<note>Of all Karuk plants the black nightshade is most like tobacco, the whites tell us.</note>
      </s>
    </paragraph>
    <paragraph>
      <s>
	<kar>
	  <w>
	    <m id="2600">imxathakêem</m></w>.</kar>
	<eng>They smell strong.</eng>
      </s>
