	    <m id="6035">tih</m>
	    <m id="1387">irak</m></w>.</kar>
	<eng>They grow more now where beans are planted.</eng>
<note>are we sure that pa-, when co-occurring with -hirak, should always be marked NOMZ?</note>
      </s>
