	    <m id="1003">axvíthirar</m>
	    <m id="4000">kunish</m></w>.</kar>
	<eng>They look like huckleberries, but the dog huckleberries are dirty looking, they are sour, the leaves also are dirty looking.</eng>
<note>are we keeping kúna vúra (#3981) as a single entry for online texts?</note>
      </s>
